<span id="L285" class="LineNr"> 285 </span>
<span id="L286" class="LineNr"> 286 </span><span class="htmlItalic">I am not sure how to pronounce it, sir. Can you help me? </span>
<span id="L287" class="LineNr"> 287 </span>
<span id="L288" class="LineNr"> 288 </span><span class="htmlItalic">‘Well, I imagine I can be of some help. I am the Director of this fine library, young man. I am also its only librarian. And these days, I am one of its few readers; my granddaughter, Anaka, being among our small army of warriors. That is her seated in front of me. Say hello, Ana.’ </span>
<span id="L289" class="LineNr"> 289 </span>
