<span id="L299" class="LineNr"> 299 </span>
<span id="L300" class="LineNr"> 300 </span><span class="htmlItalic">E-T-H-A-N-E  A-G-A-U-N-T-H-A-R-K-A-R-U-M-hyphen-N-U</span>
<span id="L301" class="LineNr"> 301 </span>
<span id="L302" class="LineNr"> 302 </span><span class="htmlItalic">The old man smirked, ‘Mythology. Interesting. How old are you again?’ </span>
<span id="L303" class="LineNr"> 303 </span>
